{"type":"message","id":"3c5f820d","parentId":"fe2e17fd","timestamp":"2026-04-06T09:40:29.505Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Here are the skills I currently support:\n\n1. **Weather**: Get current weather and forecasts for any location.\n2. **Healthcheck**: Perform security audits, SSH/update hardening, and risk posture review.\n3. **Node-Connect**: Diagnose issues with OpenClaw node connections for Android, iOS, and macOS companion apps.\n4. **Skill-Creator**: Create, edit, or audit AgentSkills.\n5. **Weather**: Get current weather and forecasts via wttr.in or Open-Meteo.\n6. **Report-Spreadsheet-Export**: Export ViewModelContract to a CSV spreadsheet file.\n7. **SCADA-Alarm-List**: Retrieve filtered alarm rows for a scope and time range with paging.\n8. **SCADA-Alarm-Summary**: Compute alarm statistics, KPIs, rates, top offenders.\n9. **SCADA-Archive-Coverage**: Check which fields on known objects are archived.\n10. **SCADA-Data-Quality**: Assess telemetry freshness, quality codes, archive gaps, and last-change behavior for known tags.\n11. **SCADA-Object-Explore**: Explore live SCADA objects and their current or configuration fields.\n12. **SCADA-Period-Aggregates**: Compute period aggregates (avg, min, max) for known object+field tags with optional bucketing.\n13. **SCADA-Point-History**: Retrieve time-series trend/history for known object+field tags over a time range.\n14. **SCADA-Point-Snapshot**: Get the value of known object+field tags at a specific past timestamp.\n\nIf you need assistance with any specific task, feel free to ask!"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-192-168-20-122-11434","model":"qwen2.5-coder:14b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775468420852,"responseId":"chatcmpl-884"}}
